だけるよう、報酬の充実等…", "…持って、やりがいを持って、非常に危険を伴う職務でもありますが、取り組んでいただく消防団員の方々を全力で御支援をしていきたいと思っております。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/313", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/331", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/334", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/336", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/338", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/340", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/343", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/367", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00420220316/402", "sentence": []}]}]}]